<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "task.dtd" []>
<task xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="cut" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:task.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Cut</title>
  <taskbody id="body">
    <context>
      <p id="cut-intro">You can cut a part of document content as an XML structure.</p>
      <p>To cut XML content, do the following:</p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step>
        <cmd>Select what you want to cut.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p><xref href="selection.xml">Select</xref> what you want to cut in the <xref href="editing-window.xml">Editing Window</xref> or <xref href="content-map.xml">ContentMap</xref>.</p>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Cut the selection.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>Cut the selection one of these ways:</p>
        </info>
        <choices>
          <choice>
            <p>Press <uicontrol>Ctrl-X</uicontrol>.</p>
          </choice>
          <choice>
            <p>Choose <menucascade>
                <uicontrol>Edit</uicontrol>
                <uicontrol>Cut</uicontrol>
              </menucascade>.</p>
          </choice>
          <choice>
            <p>Click the <uicontrol>Cut</uicontrol> button <image href="cut-button.png" align="center" placement="inline"/> on the toolbar.</p>
          </choice>
        </choices>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
</task>
